Package: kdebase-runtime
Section: kde
Architecture: all
Depends:  kdebase-runtime-bin (>= ${binary:Version}), drkonqi (>= ${binary:Version}),
 kdebase-runtime-data (>= ${binary:Version}), kde-icons-oxygen (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: runtime components from the official KDE release
 KDE (the K Desktop Environment) is a powerful Open Source graphical desktop
 environment for Unix workstations. It combines ease of use, contemporary
 functionality, and outstanding graphical design with the technological
 superiority of the Unix operating system.

Package: kdebase-runtime-bin
Section: kde
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, kdebase-runtime-data (= ${binary:Version})
Replaces: kdebase-bin (<< 3.95.0)
Description: core binaries for the KDE base runtime module
 This package contains miscellaneous programs needed at runtime by other
 KDE applications.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, and a component of the KDE base runtime module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdebase-runtime' packages for more information.

Package: kdebase-runtime-data
Section: kde
Architecture: all
Depends: kdebase-runtime-data-common | kdebase-data (<< 4:3.90.1)
Replaces: kdebase-data (<< 4:3.95.0)
Description: shared data files for the KDE base runtime module
 This package contains the architecture-independent shared data files needed
 for running KDE applications KDE applications.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, and a component of the KDE base runtime module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdebase-runtime' packages for more information.

Package: kdebase-runtime-data-common
Section: kde
Architecture: all
Replaces: kdebase-runtime-data
Conflicts: kdebase (<< 4:3.90.1)
Description: shared data files for the KDE base runtime module 
 This package contains the architecture-independent shared data files needed
 for running KDE applications KDE applications.
 .
 The files contained in this package are also part of KDE3's kdebase-data package
 and will not be installed if KDE3's kdebase-data is installed.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, and a component of the KDE base runtime module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdebase-runtime' packages for more information.

Package: drkonqi
Section: kde
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, gdb
Description: KDE crash handler
 drkonqi is the KDE crash handler, it gives information to the user when a
 KDE application crashes.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, and a component of the KDE base runtime module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdebase-runtime' packages for more information.

Package: kde-icons-oxygen
Section: kde
Architecture: all
Replaces: kdebase-data (<= 4:3.94.0-1)
Suggests: kdebase (>= 4:3.94.0-2)
Description: Oxygen icon theme for KDE4
 Oxygen is the standard icon theme for KDE4.

Package: khelpcenter
Section: kde
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: help center for KDE
 The KDE Help Center provides documentation on how to use the KDE desktop.
 .
 The htdig package is needed to build a searchable archive of KDE
 documentation.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, and a component of the KDE base runtime module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdebase-runtime' packages for more information.

Package: kdebase-runtime-dbg
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Priority: extra
Depends: kdebase-runtime (= ${binary:Version}), kdepimlibs-dbg
Description: debugging symbols for KDE base runtime module
 This package contains the debugging symbols associated with kdebase-runtime.
 They will automatically be used by gdb for debugging kdebase-runtime related
 issues.
